          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B\colon  A\to  \mathsf {Type}]]></fr:tex> is family of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link>, then the dependent sum <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
