   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001M/0</fr:addr><fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001M/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="dependent sum of propositions › forest://erct/erct-001M/0"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001M.xml" title="dependent sum of propositions" addr="forest://erct/erct-001M" type="local">dependent sum of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link></fr:link> › forest://erct/erct-001M/0</fr:title><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>We fix pairs 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen a,b\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 and 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen a',b'\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex>. By <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0035.xml" title="covariant sum of a left-cloven family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0035" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0035" /></fr:link> via <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0017.xml" title="the intrinsic left cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0017" type="local">Example <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0017" /></fr:link>, it suffices to exhibit identifications <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  a = a']]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q\colon  p_* b = b']]></fr:tex>. These are given respectively by our assumptions that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Ba']]></fr:tex> are <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link>.</html:p>
